OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Frather cloudy, with showery outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain during the evening pushing
OL,8,Fsouthwards and generally easing.
OL,9,FBecoming drier by dawn with a breeze
OL,10,Fpicking up.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA cloudy start to Sunday but
OL,13,Flargely dry. Cloud breaking by the
OL,14,Fafternoon to leave sunnier spells.
OL,15,FBreezy and feeling cooler with
OL,16,Ftemperatures below average for early
OL,17,Fto mid-May.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
